/VG> <NG>the <HEAD>Network</HEAD></NG> <VG>also helped</VG> <NG>a local <HEAD>farmer</HEAD></NG> <PG>by</PG> <VG-VBG>simply offering</VG-VBG> <NG>a third party <HEAD>opinion</HEAD></NG> <PG>on</PG> <NG>his farming <HEAD>operation</HEAD></NG>.   <NG><HEAD>Rodionoff</HEAD></NG> <VG>said sometimes</VG> all that <VG>is needed</VG> <VG>is</VG> <PG>for</PG> <NG>an impartial third <HEAD>party</HEAD></NG> <VG-INF>to come</VG-INF> <PG>in</PG> and <NG><HEAD>look</HEAD></NG> <PG>at</PG> <NG>a farm <HEAD>operation</HEAD></NG>, <VG-VBG>noting</VG-VBG> that <RG>sometimes</RG> <NG>it</NG> <VG>can be</VG> <JG>better</JG> <PG>than</PG> <VG-VBG>simply relying</VG-VBG> <PG>on</PG> <NG><HEAD>neighbors</HEAD></NG> and <NG><HEAD>relatives</HEAD></NG>' <NG><HEAD>opinions</HEAD></NG>.   <NG><HEAD>Rodionoff</HEAD></NG> <VG>said</VG> <NG>the <CARDINAL>10</CARDINAL> <HEAD>consultants</HEAD></NG> that <VG>work</VG> <PG>for</PG> <NG>the Farm Family Support Network <HEAD>work</HEAD></NG> <PG>on</PG> <NG>a part-time</NG>, <NG>on-call <HEAD>basis</HEAD></NG>, <PG>with</PG> each <PG>of</PG> <NG>the <HEAD>consultants</HEAD></NG> <VG-VBG>working</VG-VBG> out <PG>of</PG> <NG>their <HEAD>homes</HEAD></NG>. <NG>He</NG> <VG>noted</VG> that when <NG><HEAD>consultants</HEAD></NG> <VG>meet</VG> <PG>with</PG> <NG><HEAD>farmers</HEAD></NG> <NG>they</NG> <VG>typically meet</VG> <PG>at</PG> <NG>the <HEAD>farm</HEAD></NG> <NG>they</NG> <VG>will be analyzing</VG>.   <PG>In</PG> <NG>the <HEAD>Yakima Valley</HEAD></NG>, <NG>the <HEAD>organization</HEAD></NG> <VG>recently hired</VG> <NG><HEAD>Todd Hurlburt</HEAD></NG> <VG-INF>to work</VG-INF> <PG>as</PG> <NG>a <HEAD>consultant</HEAD></NG>. <NG><HEAD>Rodionoff</HEAD></NG> <VG>said</VG> <NG><HEAD>Hurlburt</HEAD></NG>, who <VG>lives</VG> <PG>on</PG> <NG>his family <HEAD>farm</HEAD></NG> <PG>in</PG> <NG><HEAD>Zillah</HEAD></NG>, <VG>has</VG> <NG>an extensive financial <HEAD>background</HEAD></NG>, <VG-VBG>having worked previously</VG-VBG> <PG>as</PG> <NG>an <HEAD>accoun